# Changelog - AK Library Management

## Version 19.0.1.0.0
- Initial release.
- Added `library.book` model with fields: Title, ISBN, Publication Date, Price, Pages, Description, Image, Category.
- Added `book.category` model.
- Added Tree, Form, and Search views for books.
- Added Tree and Form views for categories.
- Added separate menu file (`library_menus.xml`) with main menu and submenus.
- Added security access rules.
- Tested on blank Odoo 19 database.
